Subject:[CT Birds] Pegasus Ibis Stratford
The image of a Pegasus Ibis flying out from the lagoon is much more visually and mythologically intriguing than that of a Plegadus Ibis.  A Homerian slip, perhaps, and one much appreciated.  Wish I'd been there!

Steve Br (Cheshire)    
